title: Sonic Record now Deluxe 7.0
description:
Sonic RecordNow! Deluxe Suite is the state-of-the-art CD and DVD        

  mastering tool that takes the guesswork and complexity out of CD 

  and DVD burning. Also, this Suite comes with 2 additional power 

  packed programs, Simple Backup &amp; Drive Letter Access (DLA)                                                                    
  Features:                                                            
  - Make custom Audio CDs for your car or home CD player          - MP3 &amp; MP3 VBR Encoding (rip your favorite CDs)              
  - Make CDs and DVDs bootable                                 
  - Normalization and Noise reduction for audio CDs
